{"tid":1478369,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 經典金曲精選台 III","createTime":"2019-08-16T13:19:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T04:35:58.000Z","uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"213824bae1f178426a294ff862098b81a5133c0a","tid":1478369,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:19:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_qTj5WGz3g0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_qTj5WGz3g0&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0by9ZqCMvdeqZXcPvDNBnhI%3D&h=8b0eae28\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_qTj5WGz3g0</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/B9tqKC-XJUI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FB9tqKC-XJUI&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0by9ZqCMvdeqZXcPvDNBnhI%3D&h=0f7440f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/B9tqKC-XJUI</a><br />\n<br />\n1988年初，葉德嫻不滿本地唱片制度，製作求其、太多無關音樂的工作，決定轉型專心做演員。不過，羅大佑的滾石唱片在90年找她試唱《赤子》，由晚上九時錄到翌日早上六時。葉德嫻對試唱未盡滿意；但羅大佑就將這首歌收錄在《皇后大道東》大碟裏面。豈料《赤子》這首歌大受歡迎，但葉德嫻卻因此極為不滿羅大佑。<br />\n<br />\n葉德嫻多次公開表示，唱《赤子》是給羅大佑呃的，對試唱版本根本未滿意，甚至不知道會收錄出唱片。她很開心首歌大受歡迎，但就說：「我鍾意嬲佢呀，亦希望自己可以嬲，要嚟警惕自己，係個教訓，我呢啲大情大性嘅人，唔想再俾人呃。」羅大佑其實多次公開向葉德嫻表示歉意，不過葉德嫻就是如此有個性，沒有打算不再嬲羅大佑。"},{"pid":"22bc75aca48f2eb20fe288c52cca9ff51a696bcc","tid":1478369,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:21:51.000Z","msg":"費玉清 - 草原之夜<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ALedpV13seE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FALedpV13seE&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0by9ZqCMvdeqZXcPvDNBnhI%3D&h=1801fc31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ALedpV13seE</a>"},{"pid":"d45425b790c0c77ab9868129877d60130c2fdadd","tid":1478369,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:23:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pk_gHz1SpgY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fpk_gHz1SpgY&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0by9ZqCMvdeqZXcPvDNBnhI%3D&h=168d4590\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pk_gHz1SpgY</a